      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-07063'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040525_GCR_64' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-07064'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040525_GCR_65' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Crawley</span> moved Amendment Nos. 65V to 65AB:
        <q>Page 88, line 33, leave out subsection (3) and insert&#x2014;</q>
