        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_455gc' title='Col. 455GC &mdash; HL Deb 25 May 2004 vol 661 c455GC' name='column_455gc' href='#column_455gc' rel='bookmark'>455GC</a>
        <q>Page 89, line 15, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>"transferred matter" has the meaning given by section 4(1) of the <a href="/acts/northern-ireland-act-1998">Northern Ireland Act 1998</a> (c. 47) and "deals with" in relation to a transferred matter is to be construed in accordance with section 98(2) and (3) of the 1998 Act.</q>
      </p>
      
