            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_456gc' title='Col. 456GC &mdash; HL Deb 25 May 2004 vol 661 c456GC' name='column_456gc' href='#column_456gc' rel='bookmark'>456GC</a>
            have those explanatory notes, but on the other hand, it is coming non-stop, even again today. We do not have time to look at it all.
          </p>
