          <p class='first-para'>
            I am grateful to the noble Baroness. How will employers know about all that?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0661P0-07084'>
        <a name='S5LV0661P0_20040525_GCR_85'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-christine-crawley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
