        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040525_GCR_316' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 187 [<span class="italic">Power to amend enactments relating to pensions</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-07316'>
