        <q>Page 91, line 41, after "enactment," insert "Northern Ireland legislation,</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-07323'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040525_GCR_324' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
