          <p class='first-para'>
            I am grateful to the noble Baroness. I shall need to look at that provision quite carefully to see whether it is adequate. However, I would like to see some commitment or recognition of that on the face of the Bill. I may table an amendment different from the one we are considering today on the issue.</p><p>
            On the main subject we have discussed, although I think the noble Baroness said that I introduced it at great length&#x2014;
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0661P0-07374'>
        <a name='S5LV0661P0_20040525_GCR_375'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-hollis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040525_GCR_375' title='Link to this speech by Ms Patricia Hollis' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
